{"tid":1091316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國平安奪香港數碼身份服務合約　港人私隱恐送羊入虎口","createTime":"2019-04-04T04:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T09:27:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4c416fa294f237adb10b81e03a5aa281607e1351","tid":1091316,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190403-中國平安奪香港數碼身份服務合約港人私隱恐送羊入虎口\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20190403-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%AA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E6%81%90%E9%80%81%E7%BE%8A%E5%85%A5%E8%99%8E%E5%8F%A3&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvDXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=9ca5d4df\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190403-中國平安奪香港數碼身份服務合約港人私隱恐送羊入虎口</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/xp_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fxp_0.jpg&h=3f7f8c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸保險業巨擘中國平安旗下的平安科技，以所謂的&ldquo;混合雲&rdquo;部署和人臉識別組合方案奪得價值約4400萬港元的港府eID（數碼個人身份）合約，協助港府建立eID系統，為市民提供免費服務，合約為期8年半。香港部分團體關注政府建立eID後會更易掌握市民個人資料，憂慮變相成為監控手段及增加私隱外泄風險。政府強調eID本身不會儲存任何個人資料，並有多項措施保障巿民私隱。<br />\n<br />\n政府在早前公布的《智慧城市藍圖》中，提到將會免費為香港居民提供eID，讓市民能以單一的數碼身分和認證，進行政府和商業的網上交易，例如申請公屋及居屋、車牌續牌、交稅等。創科局長楊偉雄去年12月曾形容eID是一把鑰匙，與個人生物認證連繫，並希望在2021年，所有巿民可通過eID方便地使用100項電子服務。<br />\n<br />\n平安科技首席執行官陳立明2日在新聞稿表示，公司的混合雲部署和人臉識別組方案投得今次eID項目合約，&ldquo;顯示脫穎而出的技術實力&rdquo;，形容eID是本港搭建智慧城市的骨架。"},{"pid":"a09e10760cd6309aa361f169965b79af8b864190","tid":1091316,"uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"並有多項措施保障巿民私隱<br />\n之前選民資料外洩連查都唔查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605084f7cea0b2a57391bf7c83e2e9d943afdbcb","tid":1091316,"uid":4473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"玩完"},{"pid":"08c521c5ef1dcac656640cfacd90305318f62343","tid":1091316,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"唔申請，唔會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2654d64b918deea904c2f64845d9506b704765c","tid":1091316,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"605084f7cea0b2a57391bf7c83e2e9d943afdbcb","tid":1091316,"uid":4473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"睇下政府係唔係強制要你登記囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c302c516fb39907dabdd340eea0de7acfb74bb","tid":1091316,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08c521c5ef1dcac656640cfacd90305318f62343","tid":1091316,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"唔申請，唔會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"同支那寶一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8913aa1ef5c856a2efdee433e14a1e1fda50e4d","tid":1091316,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"唔擔心，一早直送北京，仲信香港政府on 9"},{"pid":"a451b8c877f40283477e3c91f2474850ab51667a","tid":1091316,"uid":51937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"保險公司做IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69af4db8b62d33fa1103da814e914f2839de6396","tid":1091316,"uid":51720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a2654d64b918deea904c2f64845d9506b704765c","tid":1091316,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu